cn.jpush.im.android.api.model

Class GroupBasicInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.jpush.im.android.api.model.GroupBasicInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupInfo

    public class GroupBasicInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    群基本信息，只包括groupId，groupName，groupDescription, flag, level, maxMemberCount，avatarMediaID等基本信息。 如果想获取详细信息使用JMessageClient.getGroupInfo(long, GetGroupInfoCallback)或者Conversation.getTargetInfo()获取GroupInfo
    Since:
    2.4.1
